#. <section class="sutta" id="sn6.13"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "sn6.13:0.1"
msgid "Saṃyutta Nikāya 6"
msgstr "Linked Discourses 6"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "sn6.13:0.2"
msgid "2. Dutiyavagga"
msgstr "2. The Second Chapter"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "sn6.13:0.3"
msgid "13. Andhakavindasutta"
msgstr "13. At Andhakavinda"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.13:1.1"
msgid "Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā māgadhesu viharati andhakavinde."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying in the land of the Magadhans at "
"Andhakavinda."

msgctxt "sn6.13:1.2"
msgid ""
"Tena kho pana samayena bhagavā rattandhakāratimisāyaṃ abbhokāse nisinno "
"hoti, devo ca ekamekaṃ phusāyati."
msgstr ""
"Now at that time the Buddha was meditating in the open during the dark of "
"night, while a gentle rain drizzled down."

msgctxt "sn6.13:1.3"
msgid ""
"Atha kho brahmā sahampati abhikkantāya rattiyā abhikkantavaṇṇo kevalakappaṃ "
"andhakavindaṃ obhāsetvā yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ aṭṭhāsi."
msgstr ""
"Then, late at night, the beautiful Brahmā Sahampati, lighting up the "
"entirety of Andhakavinda, went up to the Buddha, bowed, stood to one side,"

msgctxt "sn6.13:1.4"
msgid ""
"Ekamantaṃ ṭhito kho brahmā sahampati bhagavato santike imā gāthāyo abhāsi:"
msgstr "and recited these verses in the Buddha’s presence:"

#. </p><blockquote class="gatha"><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.13:2.1"
msgid "“Sevetha pantāni senāsanāni,"
msgstr "“One should frequent secluded lodgings,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.13:2.2"
msgid "Careyya saṃyojanavippamokkhā;"
msgstr "and practice to be released from fetters."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.13:2.3"
msgid "Sace ratiṃ nādhigaccheyya tattha,"
msgstr "If you don’t find enjoyment there,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.13:2.4"
msgid "Saṃghe vase rakkhitatto satīmā."
msgstr "live in the Saṅgha, guarded and mindful."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.334"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.13:3.1"
msgid "Kulākulaṃ piṇḍikāya caranto,"
msgstr "Walking for alms from family to family,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.13:3.2"
msgid "Indriyagutto nipako satimā;"
msgstr "with senses guarded, self-disciplined and mindful."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.13:3.3"
msgid "Sevetha pantāni senāsanāni,"
msgstr "One should frequent secluded lodgings,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.13:3.4"
msgid "Bhayā pamutto abhaye vimutto."
msgstr "free of fear, freed in the fearless."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc4"></a>
#. VAR: sarīsapā → siriṃsapā (bj, s1-3, km, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn6.13:4.1"
msgid "Yattha bheravā sarīsapā,"
msgstr "Where dreadful serpents slither,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.13:4.2"
msgid "Vijju sañcarati thanayati devo;"
msgstr "where the lightning flashes and the sky thunders"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.13:4.3"
msgid "Andhakāratimisāya rattiyā,"
msgstr "in the dark of the night;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.13:4.4"
msgid "Nisīdi tattha bhikkhu vigatalomahaṃso."
msgstr "there meditates a mendicant, free of goosebumps."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc5"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.13:5.1"
msgid "Idañhi jātu me diṭṭhaṃ,"
msgstr "For this has in fact been seen by me,"

# https://discourse.suttacentral.net/t/a-note-on-itikira-and-itihitiha/4535
#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.13:5.2"
msgid "nayidaṃ itihītihaṃ;"
msgstr "it isn’t just what the testament says."

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.13:5.3"
msgid "Ekasmiṃ brahmacariyasmiṃ,"
msgstr "Within a single spiritual dispensation"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.13:5.4"
msgid "sahassaṃ maccuhāyinaṃ."
msgstr "a thousand are destroyers of Death."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc6"></a>
#. VAR: Bhiyyo → bhīyo (si, s1-3, km, pts1-2)
msgctxt "sn6.13:6.1"
msgid "Bhiyyo pañcasatā sekkhā,"
msgstr "And of trainees there are more than five hundred,"

# = 500,000 stream-enterers?
#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.13:6.2"
msgid "dasā ca dasadhā dasa;"
msgstr "and ten times ten tens;"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.13:6.3"
msgid "Sabbe sotasamāpannā,"
msgstr "all are stream-enterers,"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.13:6.4"
msgid "atiracchānagāmino."
msgstr "freed from rebirth in the animal realm."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="pts2ed" id="pts2ed1.335"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc7"></a>
msgctxt "sn6.13:7.1"
msgid "Athāyaṃ itarā pajā,"
msgstr "And as for other people"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.13:7.2"
msgid "puññabhāgāti me mano;"
msgstr "who I think have shared in merit—"

#. <br>
msgctxt "sn6.13:7.3"
msgid "Saṅkhātuṃ nopi sakkomi,"
msgstr "I couldn’t even number them,"

#. <br>
#. VAR: ottapan”ti → ottapeti (bj) | ottappeti (pts1, mr)
msgctxt "sn6.13:7.4"
msgid "musāvādassa ottapan”ti."
msgstr "for fear of speaking falsely.”"
